metadata.name: Shadow Letters
metadata.description:
On a sunny morning in October 2022, I was walking through the streets of Cologne towards the main train station. 

The sun was starting to come up and struck the face of this building. 

The "Maredo" letters cast their long shadows that drew me in immediately. 

This is my first collaboration, and I had the pleasure of welcoming Sixstreetunder to assist with the editing. 

Artists: DracheTech11 & Sixstreetunder

Edition 1/1
